### Root Cause
The cleanup system (`scripts/cleanup-issue-status.sh`, `scripts/close-stale-prs.sh`) was **implemented and committed** (Developer Stage 1), but the `--execute` step was **never run**. Only dry-run validation was performed.

### Missing Implementation
Per SPEC-issue-cleanup.md §3.3, the cleanup system should be **integrated into heartbeat-check.sh** for periodic automatic runs. This integration is documented but not implemented.

### Missing Test
Per SPEC-issue-cleanup.md §3.4, `tests/cleanup_validation_test.cpp` should have been created as a CTest. It was NOT created.

